ntfsprogs: ntfsprogs (NTFS filesystem libraries and utilities)
ntfsprogs: 
ntfsprogs: The Linux-NTFS project aims to bring full support for the NTFS
ntfsprogs: filesystem to the Linux operating system. The Linux-NTFS ntfsprogs
ntfsprogs: package currently consists of a library and utilities such as
ntfsprogs: mkntfs, ntfscat, ntfsls, ntfsresize, and ntfsundelete (for a full
ntfsprogs: list of included utilities see man 8 ntfsprogs after installation).
ntfsprogs:
ntfsprogs: http://www.linux-ntfs.org/
